snippet: Australia captain Steve Smith believes the unlikely victory over Pakistan in the second test on Friday can galvanise his team as they brace for stiffer challenges against India at the end of the home summer....
lead_paragraph: Australia captain Steve Smith believes the unlikely victory over Pakistan in the second test on Friday can galvanise his team as they brace for stiffer challenges against India at the end of the home summer.

headline.main: Stolen Win Can Give Rebuilding Australia Belief-Smith
